| Data   | 16*N   | In       | Out      | Data                                    |
+--------+--------+----------+----------+-----------------------------------------+
| FEC    | N or 0 | In       | Out      | Forward Error Correction (optional)     |
+--------+--------+----------+----------+-----------------------------------------+
| AUX    | N or 0 | In       | Out      | Auxiliary uses (optional)               |
+--------+--------+----------+----------+-----------------------------------------+
| PCLK   | 1      | Out      | Out      |                                         |
+--------+--------+----------+----------+-----------------------------------------+
| TxClk  | 1      | In       | NA       | Comes from a PLL or other clock source, |
|        |        |          |          | not the Link Layer.                     |
|        |        |          |          | The TxClk source is usually shared      |
|        |        |          |          | among many TX slices.                   |
|        |        |          |          | May be differential                     |
+--------+--------+----------+----------+-----------------------------------------+
