+--------------+-------------------+-----------+-----------+-----------+-----------+-----------+
|              | (Gbps/wire)            | (GHz)     | (mm)      | (mm)      | (mm)      | (mm)      |
+--------------+-------------------+-----------+-----------+-----------+-----------+-----------+
